'''徐少強'''（{{lang-en|Norman Chui Shiu Keung}}，{{bd|1950年|10月16日|catIdx=C徐}}），[[香港|香港]]男演員及武術指導。

==背景==
徐少強家有一姊一兄<ref name="Norman Chui's background, print screened on 2020-5-2" />；父親是一名商人<ref name="Norman Chui's background, print screened on 2020-5-2" />。徐在香港出生<ref name="Norman Chui's background, print screened on 2020-5-2" />，早年在[[九龍|九龍]][[深水埗|深水埗]]成長，就讀昔日位於[[基隆街_(香港)|基隆街]]的嶺東中學附設小學及嶺東中學<ref>{{cite web |url=https://drive.google.com/open?id=1WA6pcteaThnFdkGwdWcTPdZQs4B2sqrU |title=Norman Chui's alma mater, print screened on 2020-5-2 |last= |first= |date= |website= |publisher= |access-date=2020-5-2 |quote=}}</ref>。中學畢業後曾任職一間洋行的收數員工<ref name="徐少強星運遲來 自嘲靠四肢揾食">{{cite news | title=徐少強星運遲來 自嘲靠四肢揾食 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%BE%90%E5%B0%91%E5%BC%B7&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2FH7zGe%2FKF%2BFF0JM1nvpwdg&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=189&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%BE%90%E5%B0%91%E5%BC%B7%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%BE%90%E5%B0%91%E5%BC%B7%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%BE%90%E5%B0%91%E5%BC%B7%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%BE%90%E5%B0%91%E5%BC%B7%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%BE%90%E5%B0%91%E5%BC%B7%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%BE%90%E5%B0%91%E5%BC%B7%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | format= |page=5 | publisher=工商晚報 | date=1979-6-1 | accessdate=2020-4-30 |quote= }}</ref>，再轉職股票行任會計文員<ref name="徐少強星運遲來 自嘲靠四肢揾食" />，負責管理金融產品。後由於覺得工作沉悶<ref name="徐少強星運遲來 自嘲靠四肢揾食" />，且得到同事鼓勵<ref name="徐少強搜狐論英雄：古龍是喝酒輸我給氣死的" />，便於1972年考入邵氏電影公司第三期訓練班當演員。出道初期是龍虎武師<ref>{{cite news | title=電視大拍武俠劇 徐少強知名度高 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%BE%90%E5%B0%91%E5%BC%B7&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2FH7zGe%2FKF%2BFLm%2FhHS2AnYS&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=28&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%BE%90%E5%B0%91%E5%BC%B7%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%BE%90%E5%B0%91%E5%BC%B7%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%BE%90%E5%B0%91%E5%BC%B7%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%BE%90%E5%B0%91%E5%BC%B7%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%BE%90%E5%B0%91%E5%BC%B7%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%BE%90%E5%B0%91%E5%BC%B7%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=3  | publisher=工商晚報 | date=1979-5-5 | accessdate=2020-4-29 |quote= }}</ref>。[[1970年代|1970年代]]流行武俠片，徐少強在電影經常以大俠形象出現。1976年參演麗的電視《七俠五義》中「展昭」一角後獲電視台賞識；對方有意羅致他由部頭合約轉為基本合約演員，但未能成事<ref>{{cite news | title=徐少強已婉拒麗的 家燕小田又再合作 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%BE%90%E5%B0%91%E5%BC%B7&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59%2F9WIUSQ5l72EqtxLjcu1K&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=236&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%BE%90%E5%B0%91%E5%BC%B7%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%BE%90%E5%B0%91%E5%BC%B7%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%BE%90%E5%B0%91%E5%BC%B7%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%BE%90%E5%B0%91%E5%BC%B7%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%BE%90%E5%B0%91%E5%BC%B7%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%BE%90%E5%B0%91%E5%BC%B7%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=15  | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1977-3-23 | accessdate=2020-5-1 |quote= }}</ref>。他翌年客串演出[[麗的電視|麗的電視]]（[[亞洲電視|亞洲電視]]前身）連續劇《[[大丈夫_(1977年電視劇)|大丈夫]]》受到矚目，遂以邵氏借將身份為[[麗的電視|麗的電視]]拍攝作品。

